David.

546
00:58:07.880 --> 00:58:09.572
Why are you hurting me?

547
00:58:17.277 --> 00:58:19.089
My face hurts.

548
00:58:20.959 --> 00:58:22.149
Why?

549
00:58:23.338 --> 00:58:27.408
Why...
Why does my face hurt?

550
00:58:28.939 --> 00:58:29.943
Baby.

551
00:58:31.624 --> 00:58:32.584
Nat.

552
00:59:06.147 --> 00:59:08.995
Come on. man.
Here we are.

553
00:59:13.474 --> 00:59:15.590
Hey. Hold on.

554
00:59:16.159 --> 00:59:17.970
Don't die on me. please!

555
00:59:18.729 --> 00:59:21.108
Dying wouldn't be
so bad right now.

556
00:59:23.678 --> 00:59:27.365
I just don't want to
become the devil's bitch.

557
00:59:31.311 --> 00:59:33.002
I'm going to do
what I got to do.

558
00:59:35.070 --> 00:59:37.492
I'm going to do
what I got to do. Okay?

559
01:00:23.557 --> 01:00:25.062
I'm sorry. Mia.

560
01:00:26.510 --> 01:00:27.591
I love you.

561
01:00:29.732 --> 01:00:33.377
# Baby. little baby

562
01:00:33.569 --> 01:00:36.492
# It's time to say goodbye

563
01:00:37.558 --> 01:00:41.366
# Baby. little baby

564
01:00:41.509 --> 01:00:44.738
# I'll miss you day and night

565
01:00:45.267 --> 01:00:47.733
# Baby. my sweet baby

566
01:00:48.874 --> 01:00:51.569
# I'll write you every day

567
01:00:52.403 --> 01:00:56.243
# Baby. don't cry. baby

568
01:00:57.044 --> 01:01:00.001
# I wish that I could stay #

569
01:01:00.765 --> 01:01:01.999
I can't do this.

570
01:01:04.716 --> 01:01:06.222
I can't do this.

571
01:01:38.932 --> 01:01:43.046
This time the only fucking
way is the hard way!

572
01:02:22.011 --> 01:02:23.746
David.

573
01:02:24.888 --> 01:02:27.112
Murderer.

574
01:02:28.761 --> 01:02:30.267
Coward.

575
01:04:27.561 --> 01:04:28.990
Eric.

576
01:04:48.429 --> 01:04:49.389
Hey. Okay?

577
01:04:52.302 --> 01:04:53.307
David.

578
01:04:55.181 --> 01:04:56.762
I missed you. man.

579
01:05:00.894 --> 01:05:03.088
You know that. buddy.

580
01:06:19.992 --> 01:06:21.181
David?

581
01:06:23.521 --> 01:06:25.059
David?

582
01:06:25.554 --> 01:06:28.631
I can't move!
I can't breathe!

583
01:06:29.122 --> 01:06:30.550
David!

584
01:06:31.232 --> 01:06:32.923
Help me!

585
01:06:34.147 --> 01:06:35.762
Help me. David!

586
01:06:36.104 --> 01:06:37.380
You're not her.

587
01:06:37.523 --> 01:06:39.105
David!

588
01:06:39.517 --> 01:06:40.478
Help me!

589
01:06:41.321 --> 01:06:42.629
You're not her!

590
01:06:49.183 --> 01:06:51.103
Why do you hate me. David?

591
01:06:53.594 --> 01:06:55.329
I know you do.

592
01:06:56.779 --> 01:06:58.546
You left home.

593
01:06:59.579 --> 01:07:01.653
You left me all alone

594
01:07:01.728 --> 01:07:03.876
with our sick mother.

595
01:07:04.029 --> 01:07:05.567
And I was just a kid.

596
01:07:07.482 --> 01:07:08.671
You made me lie.

597
01:07:10.396 --> 01:07:12.590
Every time she
screamed your name.

598
01:07:12.660 --> 01:07:14.775
I told her you were
coming to see her.

599
01:07:15.575 --> 01:07:17.845
Like you promised.

600
01:07:18.490 --> 01:07:20.181
But you never did.

601
01:07:21.521 --> 01:07:24.368
Please stop it.
I'm begging you.

602
01:07:25.779 --> 01:07:28.779
I know Mother hates you now.

603
01:07:28.849 --> 01:07:30.583
and she waits for you in hell.

604
01:07:39.702 --> 01:07:42.278
Shut up. Shut up.

605
01:07:58.999 --> 01:08:00.809
I'm so sorry.

606
01:08:04.752 --> 01:08:06.213
I should have been there.

607
01:08:08.127 --> 01:08:10.626
I should have
been there for you.

608
01:09:03.518 --> 01:09:05.176
Come on.
Please. come back.

609
01:09:11.728 --> 01:09:14.031
Come on. Mia.
Come back to me. please!

610
01:09:55.956 --> 01:09:58.148
Okay. you are at peace.

611
01:09:59.523 --> 01:10:01.335
You are at peace now.

612
01:10:26.912 --> 01:10:27.872
David?

613
01:10:34.276 --> 01:10:35.553
Mia?

614
01:10:42.102 --> 01:10:43.718
It was so horrible.

615
01:10:45.593 --> 01:10:47.666
It was so horrible.

616
01:10:48.355 --> 01:10:51.770
It's okay.
It's all over now.

617
01:10:55.068 --> 01:10:57.872
Thanks for not
leaving me. David.

618
01:11:06.115 --> 01:11:08.810
Wait here. I'm going
to get the car keys.

619
01:11:08.954 --> 01:11:10.688
Okay?
Yeah.

620
01:12:11.863 --> 01:12:12.823
David!

621
01:12:13.705 --> 01:12:15.517
Go. Please. go.

622
01:12:15.585 --> 01:12:16.543
Go!

623
01:12:16.849 --> 01:12:19.959
I'm not going to go anywhere.
I'm not going anywhere!

624
01:12:24.023 --> 01:12:26.020
Here. take the keys.
Look at me. let's go.

625
01:12:26.171 --> 01:12:27.709
Come on. Let's go.

626
01:12:33.268 --> 01:12:34.621
Get out of here.

627
01:12:35.954 --> 01:12:38.953
No! No!

628
01:12:39.099 --> 01:12:40.136
David!

629
01:12:40.979 --> 01:12:42.712
David!

630
01:12:46.080 --> 01:12:48.502
No! No!

631
01:12:48.880 --> 01:12:51.914
David! David!

632
01:13:00.580 --> 01:13:03.079
He's coming.

633
01:15:29.453 --> 01:15:31.525
Mia.

634
01:16:27.797 --> 01:16:29.336
Come here. you bitch!

635
01:17:51.190 --> 01:17:52.423
Come on.

636
01:18:47.962 --> 01:18:50.657
You're going to die here.
you pathetic junkie!

637
01:18:52.911 --> 01:18:55.486
I've had enough of this shit.

638
01:19:30.772 --> 01:19:34.110
I will feast on your soul.

639
01:19:37.063 --> 01:19:39.178
Feast on this. motherfucker!

640
01:19:50.911 --> 01:19:52.678
Die!

641
01:20:12.737 --> 01:20:14.657
Go back to Hell. bitch.

642
01:25:49.187 --> 01:25:52.035
<i>I believe I
have made a significant find</i>

643
01:25:52.102 --> 01:25:53.915
<i>in the Candarian Ruins...</i>

644
01:25:54.059 --> 01:25:56.437
<i>a volume of ancient
Sumerian burial practices</i>

645
01:25:56.515 --> 01:25:58.477
<i>and funerary incantations.</i>

646
01:25:59.045 --> 01:26:02.002
<i>It is entitled
"Naturom Demonto."</i>

647
01:26:02.152 --> 01:26:04.618
<i>Roughly translated.
"Book of the Dead."</i>

648
01:26:04.799 --> 01:26:08.640
<i>The book is bound in human flesh
and inked in human blood.</i>

649
01:26:08.942 --> 01:26:12.096
<i>It deals with demons.
demon resurrection...</i>

650
01:26:12.279 --> 01:26:14.091
<i>those forces
which roam the forest</i>

651
01:26:14.236 --> 01:26:16.080
<i>and dark bowers
of man's domain.</i>

652
01:26:16.999 --> 01:26:19.922
<i>The first few pages warn that
these enduring creatures...</i>

653
01:26:20.067 --> 01:26:22.946
<i>may lie dormant
but are never truly dead.</i>

654
01:26:23.518 --> 01:26:25.286
<i>They may be recalled
to active life</i>

655
01:26:25.398 --> 01:26:27.776
<i>through the incantations
presented in this book.</i>

656
01:26:27.929 --> 01:26:30.395
<i>It is through recitation
of these passages</i>

657
01:26:30.461 --> 01:26:31.771
<i>that the demons
are given license...</i>

658
01:26:32.419 --> 01:26:34.305
<i>to possess the living.</i>

659
01:27:06.290 --> 01:27:08.941
<i>I have seen the dark shadows
moving in the woods...</i>

660
01:27:09.089 --> 01:27:11.589
<i>and I have no doubt that
whatever I have resurrected</i>

661
01:27:11.660 --> 01:27:12.817
<i>through this book...</i>

662
01:27:12.965 --> 01:27:16.117
<i>is sure to come calling for me.</i>

663
01:27:26.620 --> 01:27:28.083
Groovy.
